  <scopecontent id="aspace_ec094a8b881c172733bee056219ddd08">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>Includes membership records, officers' reports, business papers, subscription library records, minutes of the Society's meetings and debates.  Includes receipts and letters expressing pleasure at being honored by the society.  Receipt dated December 2, 1841 from Stonewall Jackson while he was a Virginia constable, which was later given to the Franklin Society.</p>  </scopecontent>
